title: [Murkshev's Outfitting]
[Murkshev's Magic Shoppe]
description: A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the rough pine walls, and a deep red stucco ceiling rises overhead.  A worn rug sits in one corner of a polished oak floor.  There is an iron-banded wooden chest on one side of the shop and a lacquered wooden shelf on the other.
